"text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">· 掌握</span><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-weight: bold;">最经典</span><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">的社会心理学概念；</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">· 提升</span><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-weight: bold;">人际交往素养</span><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">；</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">· 掌握实际工作、生活场景中的</span><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-weight: bold;">简单技巧</span><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">；</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">· 发现矛盾产生的</span><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-weight: bold;">本质</span><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">，跳出思维</span><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-weight: bold;">陷阱</span><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">；</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">·&nbsp;迅速切换</span><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-weight: bold;">理性视角</span><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0);">，</span><span style="box-sizing: inherit; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); font-weight: bold;">摆脱不理智</span><span style="box