ica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; white-space: normal;"><img src="http://wechatapppro-1252524126.file.myqcloud.com/app80CX1DoD4392/image/ueditor/25418000_1551261974.jpg" style="box-sizing: inherit; border-style: none; vertical-align: middle; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;" class="loadingclass"/></a></p><h2 class="" style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></h2><h2 class="" style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&gt;&gt; 期待这样的你 &lt;&lt;</span></h2><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;">· <strong>心理学爱好者</strong></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;">· 对<strong>社会热点、矛盾现象</strong>感兴趣</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;">· 平时<strong>擅长观察</strong>他人行为与社会生活</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;">· 对<strong>思维判断、自身影响力</strong>有拔高需求</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em;">· 希望对社会<strong>现状的成因</strong>有更多了解</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><br/></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><br/></p><h2 class="" style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></h2><h2 class="" style="white-space: normal; box-sizing: inherit; color: rgb(73, 73, 73); font-family: -apple-system, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, Arial, &#39;Neo Heiti&#39;, sans-serif; text-align: center;"><span style="font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">&gt;&gt;经典心理学书籍推荐，全方位洞悉人性&lt;&lt;</span></h2><p><span style="font-size: 17px; white-space: pre-wrap; caret-color: rgb(17, 17, 17); background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br/></span></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center;">《津巴多普通心理学》</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center;">[美] 菲利普·津巴多 / 中国人民大学出版社</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><br/></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center;">《社会心理学》</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center;">（第8版）[美] 戴维·迈尔斯 / 人民邮电出版社</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><br/></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center;">《社会性动物》</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center;">&nbsp;[美] 埃利奥特·阿伦森 / 华东师范大学出版社</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px;"><br/></p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; text-align: center;">《亲密关系》&nbsp;</p><p style="box-sizing: inherit; margin-top: